        <Parent_String>rifles (long guns) [300037181], long guns [300222278], small arms by form [300037156], small arms [300037150], firearms [300037148], projectile weapons with explosive propellant [300208782], projectile weapons [300203727], armaments [300420324], weapons [300036926], Weapons and Ammunition (hierarchy name) [300036743], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
